{"id":167,"parent_id":158,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":167,"title":"2 Corinthians 9","subtitle":"","short_title":"2 Cor.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/9","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 9"],[".studySummary",["i","God loves and rewards a cheerful giver—Thanks be to God for His unspeakable gift."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/9.1","order":"03.10.009.18990"},["b","1"],"For as touching the ministering to the saints, it is superfluous for me to write to you:"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/9.2","order":"03.10.009.18991"},["b","2"],"For I know the forwardness of your mind, for which I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"boast"],"of you to them of Macedonia, that Achaia was ready a year ago; and your zeal hath",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"provoked"],"very many."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/9.3","order":"03.10.009.18992"},["b","3"],"Yet have I sent the brethren, lest our boasting of you should be in vain in this behalf; that, as I said, ye may be ready:"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/9.4","order":"03.10.009.18993"},["b","4"],"Lest haply if they of Macedonia come with me, and find you unprepared, we (that we say not, ye) should be ashamed in this same confident boasting."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/9.5","order":"03.10.009.18994"},["b","5"],"Therefore I thought it necessary to exhort the brethren, that they would go before unto you, and make up beforehand your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"bounty"],", whereof ye had notice before, that the same might be ready, as",["i","a matter of"],"bounty, and not as",["i","of"],"covetousness."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/9.6","order":"03.10.009.18995"},["b","6"],"But this",["i","I say,"],"He which soweth sparingly shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"reap"],"also sparingly; and he which",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"soweth"],"bountifully shall reap also bountifully."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/9.7","order":"03.10.009.18996"},["b","7"],"Every man according as he",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"purposeth"],"in his heart,",["i","so let him give;"],"not",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"grudgingly"],", or of necessity: for God loveth a",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"cheerful"],["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_7d"},"giver"],"."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/9.8","order":"03.10.009.18997"},["b","8"],"And God",["i","is"],"able to make all",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"grace"],"abound toward you; that ye, always having all sufficiency in all",["i","things,"],"may abound to every good work:"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/9.9","order":"03.10.009.18998"},["b","9"],"(As it is written, He hath dispersed abroad; he hath given to the poor: his righteousness remaineth for ever."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/9.10","order":"03.10.009.18999"},["b","10"],"Now he that ministereth seed to the sower both minister bread for",["i","your"],"food, and multiply your seed sown, and increase the fruits of your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"righteousness"],";)"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/9.11","order":"03.10.009.19000"},["b","11"],"Being enriched in every thing to all bountifulness, which causeth through us",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"thanksgiving"],"to God."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/9.12","order":"03.10.009.19001"},["b","12"],"For the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"administration"],"of this service not only supplieth the want of the saints, but is abundant also by many thanksgivings unto God;"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/9.13","order":"03.10.009.19002"},["b","13"],"Whiles by the experiment of this ministration they glorify God for your professed subjection unto the gospel of Christ, and for",["i","your"],"liberal distribution unto them, and unto all",["i","men;"]],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/9.14","order":"03.10.009.19003"},["b","14"],"And by their prayer for you, which long after you for the exceeding grace of God in you."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/9.15","order":"03.10.009.19004"},["b","15"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"Thanks"],["i","be"],"unto God for his unspeakable",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"gift"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/9.2a","order":"03.10.009.19005"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/7.14"},"2 Cor. 7:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/9.2b","order":"03.10.009.19007"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/provoking"},"TG Provoking"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/9.5a","order":"03.10.009.19009"},["b","5a"],["span.small","GR"],"gift, blessing, benevolence."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/9.6a","order":"03.10.009.19011"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/harvest"},"TG Harvest"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/9.6b","order":"03.10.009.19013"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/accountability"},"TG Accountability"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/9.7a","order":"03.10.009.19015"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/6.33.33-34"},"D&C 6:33 (33–34)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/9.7b","order":"03.10.009.19017"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hypocrisy"},"TG Hypocrisy"],"."],["div",{"id":"7c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/9.7c","order":"03.10.009.19019"},["b","7c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/cheerful"},"TG Cheerful"],"."],["div",{"id":"7d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/9.7d","order":"03.10.009.19021"},["b","7d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/generosity"},"TG Generosity"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/9.8a","order":"03.10.009.19023"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.18.15-23"},"Philip. 4:18 (15–23)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/2.19.17-19"},"Jacob 2:19 (17–19)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/grace"},"TG Grace"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/9.10a","order":"03.10.009.19025"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/righteousness"},"TG Righteousness"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/9.11a","order":"03.10.009.19027"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/thanksgiving"},"TG Thanksgiving"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/9.12a","order":"03.10.009.19029"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/13.16"},"Heb. 13:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/9.15a","order":"03.10.009.19031"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/thanksgiving"},"TG Thanksgiving"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/9.15b","order":"03.10.009.19033"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/james/1.17"},"James 1:17"],"."]]}
